data.description: What a beautiful home! Completely remodeled and located on the south side of Crestview. The kitchen features lovely solid oak cabinetry, solid surface countertops and Kenmore Elite appliances to include a smooth tope cook range. The large kitchen is open to the bright and spacious dining area with access to the screened back porch. This lovely all brick 2 story home has 4 bedrooms and 3 baths with lots of added features. The warm and inviting living room with cathedral ceiling is just waiting for you to relax in front of the gas fireplace and enjoy your favorite music or movie with the built-in surround sound system. Also featured on the main floor is the master suite with a jetted tub, double vanity, and a large walk-in closet. There is also the laundry room and an additional full bath available for your guest?s convenience. A lovely stairway leads to the landing were you can look down on the living room or visit the 3 additional bedrooms and the third full bath. This wonderful home sits on a large level lot of nearly half an acre and has a newer 3 ton Rudd A/C system, a metal roof, gutters and 2 outbuildings with electricity in the fenced back yard. Don't miss out on seeing this fantastic home, schedule your appointment today.
